    • Enum Constant Summary

      Enum Constants 
      Enum Constant and Description
      GATE_XML
      The "GATE XML" standoff XML format.
      INLINE_XML
      Annotations stored as inline XML tags.
      JSON
      JSON format based on that used by Twitter, storing the document text as a "text" property and the annotations as an "entities" property in a JSON object.
      MIMIR
      Send documents to a Mímir indexing server.
      XCES
      Standoff XML format that stores the document plain text in one file and the annotations in another.
